pan style=\"font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: medium;\">[2 marks] </span></em></strong></p>\r\n<div class='question_part_label'>c.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n","topic0":"Topic 1 - Algebra","topic1":"1.1","topic2":"Arithmetic sequences and series; sum of finite arithmetic series; geometric sequences and series; sum of finite and infinite geometric series.","ReferenceCode":"12N.2.sl.TZ0.1"}